title: Dog Diaries - Letter A (New Series!)
description:
On episode 412, we begin a new series: Dog Diaries. Very similar to Double Rainbow, we will learn about dog breeds in alphabetical order. Of course I'll include some interesting facts about each breed, and my own commentary. This episode we go over dog breeds beginning with letter A, and we preview letter B.  Enjoy!
